WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.120
The Barclays app

2
00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.908
How to replace a damaged debit card

3
00:00:08.320 --> 00:00:10.680
To replace a damaged card, log in

4
00:00:10.680 --> 00:00:13.678
and from the home screen choose ‘Your cards'.

5
00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:16.880
Select the card that needs to be replaced

6
00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:19.960
and tap ‘Report damaged, lost or stolen’.

7
00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:23.120
Then select ‘My card is damaged’.

8
00:00:23.520 --> 00:00:26.160
Check your delivery address is correct.

9
00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:30.560
You’ll be able to use your existing card
until your replacement card arrives.

10
00:00:30.760 --> 00:00:32.240
Click ‘Next’.

11
00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:36.680
If the details are correct, click on
‘Confirm new card order’.

12
00:00:37.440 --> 00:00:38.720
And you’re done.

13
00:00:38.720 --> 00:00:42.960
Your new card is on its way and will be
with you within five working days.